Module org.eclipse.persistence.core
Package org.eclipse.persistence.oxm.record

Class JsonRecord.JsonRecordContentHandler

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.persistence.oxm.record.JsonRecord.JsonRecordContentHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
ExtendedContentHandler, ContentHandler, LexicalHandler
Enclosing class:
JsonRecord<T extends JsonRecord.Level>
protected class JsonRecord.JsonRecordContentHandler extends Object implements ExtendedContentHandler, LexicalHandler
This class will typically be used in conjunction with an XMLFragmentReader. The XMLFragmentReader will walk a given XMLFragment node and report events to this class - the event's data is then written to the enclosing class' writer.
See Also:
